<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥٢٣ -<span class="c5"> وَقِيلَ:</span> عَنِ الْمُطَّلِبِ، عَنْ أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ،<span class="c5"> وَفِيهِ مِنَ الزِّيَادَةِ:</span> <span class="c2">«فَإِنَّهَا مِنْ شَعَائِرِ الْحَجِّ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>